Feature: Managing Project Teams

This feature is designed to test the main possible, but basic operations a user can perform
in order to manage project teams. Some fundamental connections/ assignments with other CDB objects
might also be tested. Further possible connections/ assignments are tested in the respective feature.

Background:
    Given a project exists
        And a person exists


Scenario Outline: Allocate A Registered User To A Project Team
    When <role> allocates this person to the project
    Then this person is <status> to the project

    Examples:
        | role            | status        |
        | Projektleiter   | allocated     |
        | Projektmitglied | not allocated |


Scenario Outline: Delete Project Team Member 
    Given the person is allocated to the project
    When <role> deletes the allocation of this person to the project
    Then the allocation of the person to the project is <status>

    Examples:
        | role            | status      |
        | Projektleiter   | deleted     |
        | Projektmitglied | deleted     |